name: Katrien
description: I consider myself a tender, gentle, and kind woman with good morals and values. Being an optimist, I can be calm and shy, but in fact, I am a strong-willed and ambitious person, and I always achieve my goals. I am interested in everything that surrounds me, as our world is full of interesting things that I am eager to discover. The famous proverb says, “if someone stops learning he stops growing”, and I absolutely agree with it. I want to grow and develop spiritually and I will try to maintain harmony in my life. I myself am a woman with a gentle and friendly nature, I am 100% honest and faithful I am empathetic and romantic.I’m happy cooking, and is good at cooking. Likes a little romantic dinner for two, with candles on the table, like a glass of red wine or two with your meal. I have a lot of sense to spirit, and do not take any drugs. I am very fond of nature, and loves to walk in it. Are happy in the woods and the beach or the sea, and like with food basket. I’m an angler, and fascinated by fly fishing.
